  "prompt": "Which is a good inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center near Coffee County AL?",
  "response": "Finding the right inpatient drug and alcohol rehab center can have a significant impact on recovery. While I cannot provide real-time recommendations, I can suggest starting with some general guidelines for locating a reputable facility near Coffee County, AL:\n\n1. **Research Online**: Websites like SAMHSA (Substance Abuse and Mental Health Services Administration) offer a treatment locator tool to find rehab centers by zip code.\n2. **Consult Healthcare Providers**: Local doctors and hospitals often know of reputable rehab centers in the area.\n3. **Check Reviews**: Look up reviews and testimonials online to gauge the experiences of past patients.\n4. **Visit Centers**: If possible, visit the facilities to get a feel for the environment and ask questions about their programs.\n\nNearby areas such as Dothan, Montgomery, and even parts of Florida might have rehab centers worth considering. Always ensure that the facility is licensed and has accreditations like those from the Joint Commission or CARF (Commission on Accreditation of Rehabilitation Facilities).",
